                    Roam Info
                </div>
                <p>Warid brings to you an SMS based service that will serve as an information log for anybody interested in roaming abroad!</p>
                <p>Through this service, customers who intend to go abroad will be able to know call, SMS or data tariffs for all mobile operators in any country they plan to visit. This would help them in deciding which operator to opt for once they land in that country.</p>
                <p>In order to avail this service, the customer will have to follow the procedure below:</p>
                <p>
                    For Postpaid Roaming Information: SMS Postpaid&lt;space&gt;Country name to 4747<br />
                    For Prepaid Roaming Information: SMS Prepaid&lt;space&gt;Country name to 4747<br />
                    For GPRS Roaming Information: SMS GPRS&lt;space&gt;Country name to 4747
                </p>
                <h2>FAQs</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        What information does this service offer?
                    </li>
                    <p>Through this service,  you   will be receiving an SMS containing roaming tariffs for local and    International calls, SMS and GPRS associated with an international   mobile operator  in the country of your choice. </p>
                    <li>
                        How much will I get charged to send an SMS?
                    </li>
                    <p>Standard SMS charges  of Rs. 2+tax apply.</p>
                    <li>
                        Can this service be availed by any Warid  customer?
                    </li>
                    <p>Yes, both  prepaid and postpaid customers can avail this service. </p>
                </ul>
                <p><strong>Sample  Procedure</strong></p>
                <p><strong>For  Postpaid </strong><strong>Roaming  Information</strong></p>
                <p>
                    SMS Text: Postpaid&lt;space&gt;Country  name<br />
                    Send to: 4747<br />
                    <em>Example:  Postpaid </em><em>France</em>
                </p>
                <p><strong>For Prepaid </strong><strong>Roaming Information</strong></p>
                <p>
                    SMS text:  Prepaid&lt;space&gt;Country  name                   <br />
                    Send to: 4747<br />
                    <em>Example: Prepaid France</em>
                </p>
                <p><strong>For GPRS </strong><strong>Roaming Information</strong></p>
                <p>
                    SMS text: GPRS&lt;space&gt;Country  name                           <br />
                    Send to: 4747<br />
                    <em>Example: GPRS France</em>
                </p>
                <p><strong><em>For further details call 321.</em></strong></p>
